Notably, a robotics startup flies a small drone above its booth to attract attention. Alumni volunteers offer quick pep talks near the coffee station, and workshops on networking etiquette are set to begin in an adjoining classroom. Additionally, healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos, while representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. Students leave the center carrying tote bags and a stack of business cards, with some comparing their swag items.
